title: Parking Tickets for 'No Stopping', Vancouver, 2004-2008
name: Parking Tickets for 'No Stopping', Vancouver, 2004-2008
description: Total Tickets issued for parking in  no stopping zones in Vancouver from  2004-2008. This dataset was uploaded by the Vancouver Sun which received the information through a FOIA request. This and Other Parking ticket data can be found through the Vancouver Sun Parking ticket database.
